com.interpss.opf

Interface OpfGen

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AclfGen, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OpfGenImpl

    public interface OpfGen
extends AclfGen
    A representation of the model object 'Base Opf Gen'. Base OPF Gen class for OPF analysis.

    The following features are supported:

    • Operating Mode
    • Coeff A
    • Coeff B
    • Fixed Cost
    • Inc Cost
    • Opf Limits
    • Capacity Limit
    See Also:
    OpfPackage.getOpfGen()
